<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Contact Submission</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; color: #333;">
  <div style="margin: auto; background-color: #ffffff; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
    <h2>Hello {{name}},</h2>

    <p>We have received your contact submission. Details:</p>

    <ul>
      <li><strong>Full Name:</strong> {{fullName}}</li>
      <li><strong>Email:</strong> {{email}}</li>
      <li><strong>Phone:</strong> {{phone}}</li>
      <li><strong>Property Address:</strong> {{propertyAddress}}</li>
      <li><strong>Note:</strong> {{note}}</li>
    </ul>

    <p>We will reach out to you soon.</p>

    <p style="margin-top: 40px;">Best regards,<br/>The <strong>{{website}}</strong> Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
